reviews.text:
Holy shit.&#xD;
&#xD;
You ever played cereal suicide? Yanno, mixing a bunch of cereals in bowl? Yeah, that's totally what I'm getting here. It's the bottom of a bowl of frosted flakes and lucky charms. Little bit of wheat, shitton of sugar, and sweet sweet milk. The mix of bavarian cream and OoO totally makes a rich sweet milk, and there's more than a hint of the lucky charms in there. Don't get me wrong, I'm totally noticing the frosted flakes, but it's that hint of lucky charms marshmallow dust that keeps pimp slapping my attention towards it. Best damned cereal milk I've ever had. And I'm hearing this from at least 4 friends I've handed it over to.&#xD;
&#xD;
Seriously, Steam, you straight killed the hell outta this!

Spot on representation of the profile! Light, sweet and tasty, definitely closer to bottom of the bowl of Frosties. Thanks for opening my eyes to that milky undertones!&#xD;
Gotta mix this if you like cereal vapes!&#xD;
 Keep up the good work üëç

Awesome recipe, I can highly recommend this one! This will certainly teach new mixers the use of Acetyl Pyrazine, Cereal 27 and milk bases in general. &#xD;
For instance, I tried substituting OOO Cream Milky Undertone 2% by FA Creme Fresh 1% and TPA Dairy Milk 1% and it works beautifully. &#xD;
5 Stars for the USA, many thx Clayton.
